==== 客运列车种别 ====
[[File:Gatimaan_express.jpg|thumb]]
印度铁路旅客列车按照停站数目、在线路上的优先级和收费标准进行分类。列车车次使用五位数编码表示，首位数为1或2表示列车为长途快速列车；首位数为0表示列车为只在某些时期开行的特别列车，收费标准不同；首位数为5表示列车为普通旅客列车。第二位数表示运营该列车的铁路区，不过快速列车的第二位数均为0或2。<ref name=irfcanumber/> 第三位数表示负责列车养护和清洁的铁路区下属分区，最后两位数则为列车序列号。<ref name="irfcanumber">{{cite web | title = The system of train numbers | work = IRFCA.org | url = http://www.irfca.org/faq/faq-number.html | accessdate = 3 June 2007 | publisher = Indian Railways Fan Club | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809063957/https://www.irfca.org/faq/faq-number.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>车次编号原先由四位数组成，于2010年10月调整为五位数。<ref name="fiveDigitNumer">{{cite web | title=New Train Number Enquiry | work=Indian Railways Passenger Reservation Inquiry | url=http://www.indianrail.gov.in/inet_trnno_enq.html | accessdate=5 February 2011 | publisher=Centre For Railway Information Systems | archive-date=2010-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124132548/http://indianrail.gov.in/inet_trnno_enq.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>首末站及途经线路相同，但方向不同的两班列车，车次编号通常为连续号码。<ref name="irfcanumber" />

旅客列车也按照运行速度进行分类。<ref name="irfcarailops">{{cite web | title = railway operations — I | url = http://www.irfca.org/faq/faq-ops.html | accessdate = 11 June 2007 | work = IRFCA.org | publisher = Indian Railways Fan Club | archive-date = 2011-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110519134729/http://irfca.org/faq/faq-ops.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>长途快速列车停站较少，大多进行了命名以便识别，名称通常与行经地区、线路有关，或是与列车相关的名人、旅游景点等。<ref name="irfcaname">{{cite web|url=http://www.irfca.org/faq/faq-name.html|title=Train names|work=IRFCA.org|publisher=Indian Railways Fan Club|accessdate=3 June 2007|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401200717/https://www.irfca.org/faq/faq-name.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="namehindu">{{cite news|url=http://www.blonnet.com/life/2005/06/24/stories/2005062400010100.htm|title=What's in a Train Name?|last=Sekhsaria|first=Pankaj|date=24 June 2005|accessdate=4 June 2007|newspaper=The Hindu Business Line|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070608015032/http://www.blonnet.com/life/2005/06/24/stories/2005062400010100.htm|archivedate=2007-06-08}}</ref>

