ways gets first model rake of luxury 'Make in India' coaches|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/infrastructure/indian-railways-gets-first-model-rake-of-luxury-make-in-india-coaches/led-reading-lights/slideshow/50527595.cms|access-date=13 January 2016|agency=Bennett, Coleman & Co. Ltd.|work=The Economic Times|date=11 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114215143/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/infrastructure/indian-railways-gets-first-model-rake-of-luxury-make-in-india-coaches/led-reading-lights/slideshow/50527595.cms|archive-date=2016-01-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Indian Railways unveils 'Make in India' train coaches with new look|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/photos/business-gallery/192582/indian-railways-unveils-make-in-india-train-coaches-with-new-look-check-irctc-co-in/2/|access-date=13 January 2016|agency=The Indian Express Group|work=The Financial Express|date=13 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115052117/http://www.financialexpress.com/photos/business-gallery/192582/indian-railways-unveils-make-in-india-train-coaches-with-new-look-check-irctc-co-in/2/|archive-date=2016-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>、引进[[全球定位系统|全球定位系统]]（GPS）并应用于列车追踪<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/business/report-just-like-your-cabs-you-can-soon-track-trains-in-real-time-via-gps-2563623|title=Just like your cabs, you can soon track trains in real time via GPS {{!}} Latest News & Updates at Daily News & Analysis|date=30 November 2017|work=DNA India|access-date=30 November 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202071947/http://www.dnaindia.com/business/report-just-like-your-cabs-you-can-soon-track-trains-in-real-time-via-gps-2563623|archive-date=2017-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>、在{{link-en|数字印度|Digital India}}带动下投资3.5兆卢比用于铁路数字化<ref name=bg1/>、在2016年11月前建成1885个[[雨水收集|雨水收集]]系统<ref name=rain1>[http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155020 Rain Water Harvesting System In Indian Railway] {{Wayback|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=155020 |date=20171223102329 }}, 7 December 2016.</ref>、铁路用地及轨道沿线造林工程<ref name=forest1>[https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/07/india-plants-50-million-trees-uttar-pradesh-reforestation/ India Plants 50 Million Trees in One Day, Smashing World Record] {{Wayback|url=https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/07/india-plants-50-million-trees-uttar-pradesh-reforestation/ |date=20171223102536 }}, [[National_Geographic|National Geographic]], July 2016.</ref>。

印度铁路还将实行铁路电气化，以节省进口燃料的费用。<ref name=bg1>[http://railengdigest.com/project-news/asia/indian-railways-converts-broad-gauge/ Indian Railways orders conversion to Broad Gauge] {{Wayback|url=http://railengdigest.com/project-news/asia/indian-railways-converts-broad-gauge/ |date=20171223102927 }}, Rail Digest, 12 April 2017.</ref>2017至2022年间，印度铁路将装备一吉瓦功率的太阳能电网和130兆瓦的风电网络，并研发独立供电的太阳能列车，此前印度在2017年6月研制了首列太阳能动车组<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Delhi/indias-first-solar-powered-demu-train-launched/article19281625.ece|title=India's first solar-powered DEMU train launched|work=The Hindu|access-date=23 July 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726225212/https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Delhi/indias-first-solar-powered-demu-train-launched/article19281625.ece|archive-date=2018-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20130808115946/http://www.eco-business.com/news/railways-iit-madras-tie-power-ac-coaches-solar-energy/ Railways, IIT-Madras tie up to power AC coaches with solar energy]. ''The Times of India'' (5 August 2013). Retrieved on 17 August 2013.</ref><ref name=solar1>[https://www.curbed.com/2017/7/19/15995536/solar-power-train-india-railways India’s new solar-powered train is the first in the world] {{Wayback|url=https://www.curbed.com/2017/7/19/15995536/solar-power-train-india-railways |date=20171223102640 }}, June 2017</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/309625965 |title=Archived copy |access-date=26 July 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726225212/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/309625965_Rail_coaches_with_rooftop_solar_photovoltaic_systems_A_feasibility_study |archive-date=2018-07-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外也有在铁路车站顶部安装太阳能板的计划<ref>{{cite news|title=NORTHERN RAILWAYS TO INSTALL 5 MW ROOFTOP SOLAR IN FOUR OF ITS STATIONS|url=http://mercomcapital.com/northern-railways-to-install-5-mw-rooftop-solar-in-four-of-its-stations#sthash.5S8zaJPl.dpuf|access-date=3 March 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303201130/http://mercomcapital.com/northern-railways-to-install-5-mw-rooftop-solar-in-four-of-its-stations#sthash.5S8zaJPl.dpuf|archive-date=2017-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。印度铁路与[[阿尔斯通|阿尔斯通]]开展的一项价值2000亿卢比的合作项目，将在2018至2028年间为印度供应800台电力机车。<ref name="Economic Times"/>

截至2019年1月，印度铁路已移除所有宽轨线路上的无人值守道口，铁路立体化正在大规模推进<ref name=umc1>[https://pib.gov.in/Pressreleaseshare.aspx?PRID=1575836 All unmanned level crossings (UMLCs) on Broad Gauge (BG) have been eliminated on 31st Jan 2019.] {{Wayback|url=https://pib.gov.in/Pressreleaseshare.aspx?PRID=1575836 |date=20160611154206 }}, 12 May 2016.</ref><ref name=bg1/>。此外还有其他保障运输安全的计划，例如在所有空调车厢上安装火灾自动报警系统<ref>{{cite web|title=Indian Railways develops Automatic Fire and Smoke Detection System|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/09/indian-railways-develops-automatic-fire-and-smoke-detection-system/|access-date=5 September 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908145221/http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/09/indian-railways-develops-automatic-fire-and-smoke-detection-system/|archive-date=2013-09-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

